%N A395659 Expansion of (Sum_{k>=0} binomial(4*k,k) * x^k)^5.
%F A395659 a(n) = Sum_{i,j,k,l,m >= 0 and i+j+k+l+m=n} binomial(4*i,i) * binomial(4*j,j) * binomial(4*k,k) * binomial(4*l,l) * binomial(4*m,m).
%F A395659 G.f.: B(x)^5 where B(x) is the g.f. of A005810.
%F A395659 a(n) = Sum_{k=0..n} 3^k * binomial(k+3,3) * binomial(4*n+4,n-k).
%o A395659 (PARI) a(n) = sum(k=0, n, 3^k*binomial(k+3, 3)*binomial(4*n+4, n-k));
